title: Jonathan Danty
text: Jonathan Danty (born 7 October 1992) is a <a href="French%20people">French</a> <a href="rugby%20union">rugby union</a> player. He plays at <a href="centre%20%28rugby%20union%29">centre</a> for <a href="Stade%20Fran%C3%A7ais">Stade Français</a> in the <a href="Top%2014">Top 14</a>.
